data.description: Come home to your own little piece of heaven on earth!  As you approach this hidden gem, you'll feel that sense of peace and an awareness that this place is special.  The log home is so charming with its full wrap-around porch and lifetime metal roof, and when you step inside, you'll feel like it's Christmas everyday surrounded by the warm ambience of real wood!  And as you sip your coffee by the pond, hearing only the leaves rustling, birds chirping and other sounds of nature, you'll breathe easy and relax, knowing that this home is yours.  There's almost 5 acres to create your own field of dreams.  A slab is already in place if you want to rebuild a barn there and bring your animals.  The covered carport could serve any number of functions, including a summer kitchen if you choose.  You'll find room to roam with the freedom to create!  In 2020, the seller installed a full new 5-ton A/C system (including ductwork) and beautiful exterior doors.  Propane tank serves only the generator.
